    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk, it still feels super weird. it's almost like there's some sort of invisible force or... i don't know, something mischievous happening behind the scenes that we just can't see. is there any part of physics that deals with stuff being that unpredictable or \"tricky\" like that?",
      "source": "evaluator"
